Playing my own trick-shot version of corn hole 🌽  🕳️  in the field this summer ☀️  🕶️ ! 

Enjoying some #Sleemanbeer while getting creative with the #Sleemanhackpack game! Had an absolute blast tossing the bean bags around and kicking back with @sleemanbeer 

#sponsored - “closed beer cans used as props only, Please drink responsibly”
